/*
 * Generate Hyperlambda code that converts a value to a short integer type.
 * The code should take a source node with a value and convert it to a short integer.
 * 1. [convert] - This slot converts the value of the node it points to, to a specified type.
 * 2. [type] - Specifies the target type for conversion, which is "short" in this case.
 */
.value:5
convert:x:@.value
   type:short